NAME
    Ledger::Command - Wrapper class for the ledger command line utility

VERSION
    version 0.000001

SYNOPSIS
        use Ledger::Command;
        my $ledger = Ledger::Command->new('/usr/local/bin/ledger');
        $ledger->file('your-ledger.dat');
        my $balance = $ledger->balance(account_regex => '^Assets');

SEE ALSO
    *   Ledger <http://www.newartisans.com/software/ledger.html>

